{"tid":1832763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★近期286間公司涉及裁員，有近20%員工被僱主拖欠薪金","createTime":"2020-01-21T11:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T05:08:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4603f19b5444bb4b5c08e16c4beae33d9793183a","tid":1832763,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"勞聯指近期接獲數百宗裁員個案，涉及公司達286間，有超過600名員工被裁，其中有近20%員工被僱主拖欠薪金，欠薪總額超過260萬，部分員工被欠薪近1年，批評現行的破欠基金未能向僱員提供有效保障，有違基金目的。<br />\n<br />\n從事飲食業的關先生指去年兩次被拖欠薪金，涉近10萬港元，至今仍未收到任何破欠基金，但向勞審處遞交文件等已花費4000港元作影印費等開支。他是一家四口的經濟支柱，母親及弟弟是長期病患，平時只能一日食一餐及以即食麵度日。<br />\n<br />\n從事泥水工作的工友表示自去年8月，連同其他工友被拖欠共78.5萬港元，至今分毫未收。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200121/bkn-20200121150958139-0121_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200121%2Fbkn-20200121150958139-0121_00822_001.html&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6oaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=fd9978fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200121/bkn-20200121150958139-0121_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3aad83432e5315e6289acb7c8f331520a0e9683b","tid":1832763,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200121/photo/bkn-20200121150958139-0121_00822_001_02b.jpg?20200121165254\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200121150958139-0121_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20200121165254&h=63845503&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb19f0b381f930d806fb7ee482d3a751b3d77cca","tid":1832763,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黃圈嚇下人嘅姐 唔會執粒嘅"},{"pid":"c5357629645cc1d7b8efd9b39533ef5bfd1f9ac2","tid":1832763,"uid":152516,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:46:20.000